channel.title: Some new electronic tunes ♪
channel.description:
Hey guys, long time no see; haven't visited since Black Mesa launched although spent a lot of time here on the countdown before hand, was also here for that forum reset we had ;~;
Thought I'd pop in to share 2 new songs I've created, thought someone here might dig it.

item.description:

Well produced. I enjoyed both of these. Do you have a soundcloud that contains more? Also, what DAW do you use?

Thanks, glad you like them! I released my first EP a little while ago with a bunch of stuff on there over here - https://indeimaus.bandcamp.com/album/insanity

All the songs are free to listen to on Youtube as well, these 2 songs are off my first actual album : )
